<!DOCTYPE task PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Task//EN" "task.dtd" []>
<task xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="changing-local-related-link-into-external-related-link-to-newly-created-document" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:task.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Changing Local Related Link into External Related Link to Newly-Created Document</title>
  <taskbody>
    <context>
      <p>To change a local related link into an external related link to a newly-created document, do the following:</p>
    </context>
    <steps>
      <step conref="changing-the-target-of-local-related-link.xml#changing-the-target-of-local-related-link/place-cursor-in-related-link">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
      <step conref="changing-the-target-of-local-related-link.xml#changing-the-target-of-local-related-link/step-call-change-local-related-link-dialog">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
      <step conref="changing-local-related-link-into-external-related-link-to-existing-document.xml#changing-local-related-link-into-external-related-link-to-existing-document/step-select-external-link-tab">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
      <step conref="inserting-external-xref-to-newly-created-document.xml#inserting-external-xref-to-newly-created-document/step-call-create-new-dita-document-dialog">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
      <step conref="inserting-external-xref-to-newly-created-document.xml#inserting-external-xref-to-newly-created-document/create-new-dita-document">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
      <step id="target-selected-automatically">
        <cmd>The target is selected automatically.</cmd>
        <info>
          <p>In the <uicontrol>Change External Related Link Dialog</uicontrol>, the newly-created document on the <uicontrol>Files</uicontrol> list and its top-level topic on the <uicontrol>Targets</uicontrol> list are automatically selected for insertion.</p>
          <image href="change-external-related-link-dialog-new-target-selected.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step conref="inserting-external-related-links-to-newly-created-documents.xml#inserting-external-related-links-to-newly-created-documents/specify-attributes">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
      <step conref="changing-the-target-of-local-related-link.xml#changing-the-target-of-local-related-link/change-related-link">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
      <step conref="changing-the-target-of-local-xref.xml#changing-the-target-of-local-xref/step-close-dialog-on-change">
        <cmd/>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
</task>
